title: There's a lot to love at HANA Apartments! 1 Bed, 1 Bath!
posting_body: ['HANA Apartments', 'Located at: 101 6th Ave S Seattle, WA 98104', 'Featured unit: 1 bed | 1 bath | 459 - 494 sq ft', 'Prices start at: $1490 - $1560/month', 'Call Today!', 'show contact info', 'Seattle apartments are not created equally - and HANA Apartments are a cut above the rest where urban style meets smartly designed affordability in a 4-Star, Built Green community.', 'City and water views are just the beginning of what you can expect when you choose a studio, one-, or two-bedroom floor plan at HANA Apartments.', 'Wonderful Amenities!', '✓ Accepts Electronic Payments', '✓ Bike Storage', '✓ Controlled Access', '✓ Lounge', '✓ Online Leasing', '✓ Onsite Maintenance', '✓ Onsite Management', '✓ 3-Star Built Green', '✓ Barbecue Pits for Cooking Out on the Roof Deck', '✓ Controlled Access Bike Storage', '✓ Controlled Access Building', '✓ Controlled Access Rentable Parking', '✓ Convenient State of the Art Laundry Rooms', '✓ Resident Lounge and Full Kitchen with WiFi located off the Roof Deck', '✓ Roof Deck with City and Water Views', 'Apartment Features!', '✓ Brand New Appliances', '✓ Hard Surface Counters', '✓ Hardwood Style Flooring', '✓ Kitchen', '✓ Rentable Washer and Dryer', '✓ Washer and Dryer Hook-Ups', '✓ Water, Sewer, and Trash Included in Rent', '✓ Wi-Fi', '✓ City Views in Select Homes', '✓ Energy Efficient', '✓ Large Windows', '✓ Modern Finishes', '✓ Smart Layouts', '✓ Water View in Select Homes', '✓ Wood Inspired Flooring', 'show contact info', 'Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Terms:', '12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month, 17-Month, 18-Month', 'Pet Policy:', 'HANA Apartments is a pet-friendly community.', 'We allow two (2) pets max per household.', '$35/pet rent and a $300 pet deposit.', 'Weight limit: 25 lbs.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'CA460612AAFD40E']
